OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FTurning
OL,6,Fincreasingly cloudy from the west as a
OL,7,Fband of rain moves eastwards overnight
OL,8,Facross all areas by the early hours.
OL,9,FFeeling cool in the strengthening
OL,10,Fsoutheasterly breeze.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTuesday:FCloudy and breezy, with rain
OL,13,Fclearing to the east during the
OL,14,Fmorning. Followed by frequent heavy
OL,15,Fshowers in the afternoon before easing
OL,16,Finto the evening.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
